\begin_layout Subsection*

\lang english
1.
 Purpose
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard

\series bold
\lang english
Policy 4.03
\series default
 governs the Containment phase of the ECIO six-phase incident response lifecycle:
 Preparation → Identification → Containment → Eradication → Recovery → Lessons Learned.
 It establishes the decision framework the Incident Commander uses to select a containment approach,
 defines the mandatory criteria for that selection,
 and governs the playbooks that guide technical response staff through containment execution for each incident type recognized by the ECIO classification system.
\end_layout

